---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service — Postmarked">
  <main class="frame py-12 md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-prose mx-auto">

      <div class="mb-10">
        <h1 class="display text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-4">Terms of Service</h1>
        <p class="lede lede-body text-base">
          Effective Date: May 25, 2026
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-8">

        <section class="card-flat">
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
            Welcome to Postmarked. By accessing or using the Postmarked website and services, you agree to these Terms of Service.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="card-flat">
          <h2 class="display text-xl mb-3">Service Description</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
            Postmarked is a travel-sharing platform that allows users to create and share travel updates, trip posts, photos, location check-ins, and related content with friends, family, and subscribers.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="card-flat">
          <h2 class="display text-xl mb-3">Eligibility</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
            You must be at least 13 years old to use Postmarked.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed mt-3">
            By using the service, you represent that you are legally permitted to use the platform under applicable laws.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="card-flat">
          <h2 class="display text-xl mb-3">Accounts</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
            Users are responsible for maintaining the security of their accounts and credentials.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed mt-3">
            You are responsible for all activity that occurs under your account.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="card-flat">
          <h2 class="display text-xl mb-3">User Content</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
            Users retain ownership of content they upload to Postmarked.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed mt-3">
            By posting content, you grant Postmarked a limited license to store, display, and distribute the content solely for the purpose of operating the service.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed mt-3">
            Users are solely responsible for the content they upload and share. Users may not upload or distribute:
          </p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed list-disc list-inside space-y-1 mt-2">
            <li>Illegal content</li>
            <li>Spam or malicious content</li>
            <li>Content that infringes intellectual property rights</li>
            <li>Harmful, abusive, or fraudulent material</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="card-flat">
          <h2 class="display text-xl mb-3">SMS Notifications</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
            Users may choose to opt in to SMS notifications. By opting in, users consent to receive SMS messages related to Postmarked travel updates, notifications, and account activity.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed mt-3">
            Message frequency varies. Message and data rates may apply.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed mt-3">
            Users may opt out at any time by replying STOP, CANCEL, UNSUBSCRIBE, END, QUIT, REVOKE, OPTOUT, or STOPALL. Users may reply HELP for assistance.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed mt-3">
            Consent to receive SMS messages is not a condition of using the Postmarked platform.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed mt-3">
            Users can also manage their notification preferences at any time in their account settings.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="card-flat">
          <h2 class="display text-xl mb-3">Acceptable Use</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">Users agree not to:</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
            <li>Abuse or disrupt the service</li>
            <li>Attempt unauthorized access to systems or accounts</li>
            <li>Interfere with platform operation or security</li>
            <li>Use the service for unlawful activity</li>
            <li>Use automated systems to scrape, spam, or overload the platform</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="card-flat">
          <h2 class="display text-xl mb-3">Termination</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
            We reserve the right to suspend or terminate accounts that violate these Terms or misuse the platform.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="card-flat">
          <h2 class="display text-xl mb-3">Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
            Postmarked is provided on an "as is" and "as available" basis without warranties of any kind.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed mt-3">
            We do not guarantee uninterrupted availability, reliability, or error-free operation.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="card-flat">
          <h2 class="display text-xl mb-3">Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
            To the fullest extent permitted by law, Postmarked and its operators shall not be liable for indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages arising from use of the service.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="card-flat">
          <h2 class="display text-xl mb-3">Changes to These Terms</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
            We may update these Terms from time to time. Continued use of the service after updates become effective constitutes acceptance of the revised Terms.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="card-flat">
          <h2 class="display text-xl mb-3">Contact</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
            For questions regarding these Terms of Service, contact:{' '}
            <a href="mailto:support@werehere.app" class="text-ember hover:text-ember-2 transition-colors">support@werehere.app</a>
          </p>
        </section>

      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 pt-6 border-t border-line-soft text-center">
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-ghost btn-sm">← Back home</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
